This is Perl module AnyEvent::Twitter.

INSTALLATION

AnyEvent::Twitter installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan AnyEvent::Twitter

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

AnyEvent::Twitter documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc AnyEvent::Twitter

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

NOTE

The API of this module is different from older version.
Be careful to upgrade if you are using older version.

punytan
